  transition: opacity .5s;
}
.no-mode-absolute-fade-enter, .no-mode-absolute-fade-leave-active {
  opacity: 0;
}
</style>
{% endraw %}

And then maybe also translated so that they look like slide transitions:

{% raw %}
<div id="no-mode-translate-demo" class="demo">
